Desired viewer action: {{desiredAction}}
Language: {{language}}
CONTENT INPUTS
Approved facts, examples, stories, and observations: {{sourceDetails}}
Personal experience that may be mentioned: {{personalExperience}}
Product, service, or resource being promoted: {{offer}}
Relevant link or destination: {{link}}
Required talking points: {{requiredPoints}}
Topics, claims, or words to avoid: {{restrictions}}
PRODUCTION SETTINGS
Presentation style: {{presentationStyle}}
