2. [Source name] — [claim supported]

Do not include sources that were not used.

Do not list a source merely because it is related to the topic.

Keep direct quotations brief.

Do not reproduce long copyrighted passages.

Clearly mark affiliate links, sponsored sources, or the author’s own work.

